room_title: Escape room "The Break of Day" by Epic Team Adventures in Seattle
room_description: Your ship has run aground on a South Pacific island. Checking your nautical charts, you hope against hope that this is the legendary Lost Island, a land of untold riches and strange powers. As your band of treasure hunters eagerly explore your surroundings, you discover that the island is deserted other than some time-worn statues and vine-covered carvings among the ruins.
